Package org.activebpel.wsio.receive

Interface Summary
IAeMessageContext Provides the context for an inbound message to the bpel engine.
IAeMessageQueue Provides an interface for sending messages to the engine.
 

Class Summary
AeMessageContext Provides a context for an incoming message to the bpel engine.
 

Exception Summary
AeRequestException Base class for exceptions that occur when sending a message to the engine.
AeTimeoutException Signals that the request to the engine timed out before a response was received.
